  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tas Pagalms preekſch\nGr.ta Namma / bija diwidefmite\nOhlektchu Gaxrumâ / pehz ta\nNammâ Plattumu/ un deﬁmits\nOhlekschu Plattuma preekſch ta\nNamma.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch darrija tam\nNammam Lohgus / kas jawá\nweenâ Puﬀê platti / un ohtrá\nſchauri bija.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un apkahrt pee ta Nam-\nma Seenas taiſija wiꞥſch Kam-\nbarns/ abbejá Namma Seenas\npuﬀê aptkahrt/ tik labbi ap to\nNaimmu / ka arri ap to wiſt-\nfwehtaku Weetu : Ta darrija\nwiꞥſch Sahnú-Kambarns ap-\nkahrt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tahs appakſchajas Kam-\nbarn Rindas Plattums bija pee-\nzas Ohlektis/ un tahs widdejas\nPlattums feſchas Ohlektis / un\ntahs trefchas Plattums ſepti-\nnas Ohlektis / jo wiꞥſch likke\nSihjas us Abrapuffi ta Nam-\nma apkahrt / ka tee pee paſcha\nNamna Seenahm ne turrejahs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un kad tas Nams tappe\nuſtaifihhs/ tappe tas ar gatta-\nweem Akmiſeem/ kas ta atwesti\nbiia/ taiſihts / ta ka ne kahds ſes ar Zeedra Galdeem / no\nWefters nedg Ziriwis / jeb kahds\nDselses Rihks dsirdehts ktua tai\nNammá/ kad tas taiſihts tappe.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un weenas Durwis us to\nwiddeju Kambarn Reift bija pa\nlabbo Puﬀi ta Namma/ unzaur\nappatahun Treppehm bij ja-us-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta uſtaifija wiꞥſch t\nNammu/ un pabeidse to/ nn ap\nfitte to Nammu ar Zeedra Ga\nbeem/tik labbi angſcham/ ka pe\nSeenahm.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Wiꞥſch pataifija arridsa\nweenu Mahrgu us wiﬀu Nam\nmu apkahrt/ peezas Ohlektis b\nja wiꞥſas Angstums/ un stipr\nnaja to pee ta Namma ar Ze\ndra-Kohkeem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad notifke ta KUNG\nWahrds us Salamanu / tazz\ndams:\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Schis lai irr tas Name\nko tu uſtaifsi: Ja tu eeſch ma\nueim Likkumeem staigafi / u\nmannas Teefas darriji/ un wi\ntus mannuß Bauslus turrefi\npehz teem statgadams/ tad a\nstiprinafchu es fawn Wahr\nd pee tewis/ ko es us tawu Tehw\nDahwidu eſmu runnajs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un es dſthwoſchn Israei\nWiddü/ un ne atſtafchu namu\nIsraeta Landis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta uſtaifija Salaman\nto Nammu/ un pabeidse to.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Wiꞥſch arri taiſija\nNamma Seenas no Eekſchpu\nNamna Grihdi lihds Greesteen\nun apklahje to ar (Zeedra) Ro\nku Eekſchpuﬀê/ un likke ta Nam\nma Grihdi ar Preedes Galdeen\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch taiſija we\ndiwidefmits Ohlektis ar Zeed\nGaldeem pakkat to Nammu/\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
